data.description: Move in ready home 6 bedrooms, room too spread out. Large corner lot almost 1/2 acre, with a fenced in backyard. All appliance stay. Newer 200 amp electrical service, furnace ,central air and 50 year shingle roof that was installed before sellers purchased the home. Large eat in kitchen with pantry. 2 sheds out back for all of your extra storage and lawn equipment. Home is on slab, garage was converted into living space.
